creator: D&S Developers
descriptionHtml:
Chart Maker/Graph Maker allows you to create charts and graphs easily. You simply enter your data in a table and Chart Maker will create bar chart, pie chart, stack chart, line chart, area chart, radar chart or bubble chart for you.

Chart Maker/Graph Maker support conversion of one chart to another chart.
For example you can convert bar chart to line chart, area chart, stack chart, pie chart, radar chart, bubble chart or to any other chart.

This current version of chart maker support seven chart types:
1) bar chart
2) pie chart
3) line chart
4) area chart
5) radar chart
6) stack chart
7) radar chart

You can add as many data as you want, there is no limit on data input.

cloning the chart option is also available.
descriptionShort: With chart maker you can make bar chart, pie chart, line chart and much more...
